" China Daily "
-- China produces 370 million watches and 210 million clocks a year , making it the world 's largest maker of timepieces .
-- Legislation is urgently needed to guarantee the healthy development of leasing businesses in China .
The leasing sector has boomed over the past few years , covering housing , household electronic appliances and computers , automobiles , aircraft , and machinery and equipment .
